## Database Schema
products: id, name, cas, smiles, mw, purity_options[], image_url, created_at
quote_requests: id, product_id, name, email, institution, quantity, vial_size, purity, message, status, created_at
RLS enabled with public read (products) and public insert/read (quote_requests)

## Code Standards
- Use 'use client' for forms/interactions/search
- Server components by default where possible
- TypeScript strict mode always
- Supabase pattern: const { data, error } = await supabase.from('table').select('*')
- Tailwind utilities only (NO inline styles)
- Mobile-first responsive design
- Wrap useSearchParams in Suspense (Next.js 14 requirement)

## Chemical Data Format
- CAS: Badge with gold background, monospace font
- MW: Include "g/mol" unit
- Purity: "≥95%" format with teal tags
- SMILES: Monospace in grey box
- Structures: SVG in public/structures/

## CRITICAL Legal Requirements
- "Research Use Only" disclaimers on ALL product pages
- Footer with company registration (MBS, OIB, court) on every page
- GDPR compliance in Privacy Policy
- Croatian law compliance in Terms
- NO claims for human/veterinary use EVER

## Always Include
- Mobile responsive design
- Error handling + loading states + empty states
- TypeScript types (no any/unknown)
- Accessibility (labels, semantic HTML, ARIA)
- Professional, scientific tone (B2B audience)
- Company registration info visible

